                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18300527-208-off1097 t18300527-208-crimeloc1099"></join> - I did not feel it taken, but I heard a noise, looked round, and saw the prisoner in custody; this is the handkerchief - it has my initials on it; I had used it when I was in Chiswell-street, about a quarter of a mile from where I lost it.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18300527-208-person1716">
